        <hl1>The Smart Set</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>At a time when the almighty dollar and MTV define culture, it is refreshing to know that students like these are not only out there, but in an interesting way, defining a new ''hip.''</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>At a time when the almighty dollar and MTV define culture, it is refreshing to know that students like these are not only out there, but in an interesting way, defining a new ''hip.''</p>
        <p>I should know; I'm a nerd, too. I exchanged summers in the sun for long hours in research labs. But today, I am the master of my universe and very proud of my accomplishments. So hang tough brainiacs, because in tomorrow's world, the motto will be ''I think . . . therefore I win!''</p>
        <p>As an aside, Room 256 has an interesting number -- it is 2 to the 8th power!</p>
        <p>John J. Nosta</p>
        <p>Perth Amboy, N.J.</p>
      </block>
